{"id":244658,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-四川古蔺农民曾正琴住房遭遇政府带领数/","date":"2012-08-02T12:46:23Z","modified":"2012-08-02T12:46:23Z","title":"维权网 | 四川古蔺农民曾正琴住房遭遇政府带领数百人强拆（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李飞虎报道）泸州市古蔺县农民曾正琴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(13982495069)</span><span>投诉称：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日早晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>分</span><span>，古蔺县奢乡社区映月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>社村民曾正琴刚刚起床，就被一伙身着迷彩服的不明身份人限制人身自由，强行拖出自己的居住地后，其家中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多人全部被这伙人从床上抓起来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>强行拖到家门口的公路旁边。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span></div>\n<div><span>此时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>曾正琴发现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>古蔺镇副镇长李恒、镇党委书记刘体文、县检察院的王宇、国土局徐平、公安局副局长付旭等人带领约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600~700</span><span>名不明身份人员，没有出具任何证件和合法手续，开着挖掘机、汽车，强行将她家的房屋推毁，其家里喂养的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>头生猪、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>多只鸡、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多只鸭子和鹅、两只羊全部被抢走，家里的所有财产也全部被抢走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大约三小时时间，她家的合法房屋被夷为平地，财产牲畜全部被抢，土地菜园全部被毁。事发后，邻居和曾正琴的律师先后打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，但当地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>拒绝出警。曾正琴见自己的合法房屋被毁，绝望之下晕倒过去，被送往古蔺县医院抢救。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>房屋被毁后，邻居们试图帮助曾正琴照相取证，但人被控制，抢走相机手机。事发后，曾正琴的儿子，妹妹和邻居去找镇党委书记刘体文理论，被刘体文指使手下殴打，先后有曾正琴（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13982495069</span><span>）的儿子邬芝鸣、侄儿曾宣、侄儿曾双双、侄女曾巧芳（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13079188795</span><span>）、三哥曾正帮（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15183047258</span><span>）妹妹曾正会（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13919774235</span><span>）被殴打受伤，她八十岁的母亲雷启珍（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">182830741050</span><span>）也被殴打住院，至今还住在医院治疗，邻居任云林、骆国叶（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18982450186</span><span>）、朱国荣（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13398280123</span><span>）、祝仁英、刘贵英、张天会（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15283060406</span><span>）等人均被打伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另外邻居的小孩刘雨杰、刘贵英也被限制人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>曾正琴的合法房屋被强行拆毁后，至今没有任何政府部门承认是政府行为，但报警时警察却口头说是政府行为，但又拒绝提供是政府行为的书面材料。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div><span>据了解：泸州古蔺政府为了搞政绩工程</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>强行欲将农民的土地和房屋拆毁搞</span><span> </span><span>“新城改造”，将土地化整为零骗取批文，给农民的征地补偿每亩良田只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10000</span><span>元的补偿，而农民的住宅只给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>多元每平米的赔偿还包括装修费和奖励搬迁费，同时，买给农民的安置房却还要收取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>元的购买费，并且每个人只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>平米是按照这个价格给，多出的价格要按照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2700</span><span>多元购买，等于抢劫农民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>一位姓张村民这样对本网信息员说：“你自己算算账，拆房子是装修了的连装修费才总共给你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>多元，而你去买却要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>元，等于说把我的房子拆了，我还要添四百多元，才能买回来，而且还只能买回来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>平米，多出的要添</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>元才能买回来，而且还是毛坯房，装修下来每个农民每平方要损失</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span>元左右，这样的搬迁政策不等于是抢劫吗？”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因很多村民拒绝签字，政府就采取这种不明不白的方式强行拆除老百姓的房屋，据当地多位村民反映，古蔺像这样被强拆的农民进千户，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多人因此被判刑和拘留。上万农民的土地被强征，却哭诉无门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-6poXJ36mBqU/UBphNb5W2rI/AAAAAAAAKkU/4_OufZGvWRA/s1600/%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%90%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%82%BB%E5%B1%85.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"203\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-6poXJ36mBqU/UBphNb5W2rI/AAAAAAAAKkU/4_OufZGvWRA/s320/%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%90%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%82%BB%E5%B1%85.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>被限制自由的曾正琴一家及其邻居</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-N4d-NDuIzjU/UBphUL5FDVI/AAAAAAAAKkc/I8tn8uzRqhU/s1600/%E7%A9%BF%E7%9D%80%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%93%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E4%BC%9A.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-N4d-NDuIzjU/UBphUL5FDVI/AAAAAAAAKkc/I8tn8uzRqhU/s320/%E7%A9%BF%E7%9D%80%E7%9D%A1%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%93%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E4%BC%9A.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>穿着睡衣被抓起来的曾正会</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3lDPhlj9938/UBphny2LUGI/AAAAAAAAKkk/ZoE2xdFz2pw/s1600/%E5%B8%A6%E9%98%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E4%BB%AC.jpeg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3lDPhlj9938/UBphny2LUGI/AAAAAAAAKkk/ZoE2xdFz2pw/s320/%E5%B8%A6%E9%98%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E4%BB%AC.jpeg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>带队的官员们</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nbtqCL4T1hg/UBph_ynHfnI/AAAAAAAAKks/DtmgA-MSqng/s1600/%E6%AF%81%E5%9D%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF+(2).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nbtqCL4T1hg/UBph_ynHfnI/AAAAAAAAKks/DtmgA-MSqng/s320/%E6%AF%81%E5%9D%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF+(2).jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-W5w_m21doD8/UBpiNCCW34I/AAAAAAAAKk0/0aiRT4CeJGY/s1600/%E6%AF%81%E5%9D%8F%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%90%B4%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-W5w_m21doD8/UBpiNCCW34I/AAAAAAAAKk0/0aiRT4CeJGY/s320/%E6%AF%81%E5%9D%8F%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%90%B4%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>毁坏曾正琴房屋的场景</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-N0kIokiq1F0/UBpidU5hahI/AAAAAAAAKk8/j4UsWYFO8As/s1600/%E5%BC%80%E8%BD%A6%E6%8A%A2%E5%8A%AB%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%90%B4%E5%AE%B6%E8%B4%A2%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-N0kIokiq1F0/UBpidU5hahI/AAAAAAAAKk8/j4UsWYFO8As/s320/%E5%BC%80%E8%BD%A6%E6%8A%A2%E5%8A%AB%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E7%90%B4%E5%AE%B6%E8%B4%A2%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hn4FcPOVJcU/UBpijI0A3GI/AAAAAAAAKlE/CLr9mK48r_s/s1600/%E4%B9%8C%E8%8A%9D%E9%B8%A3%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B51.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hn4FcPOVJcU/UBpijI0A3GI/AAAAAAAAKlE/CLr9mK48r_s/s320/%E4%B9%8C%E8%8A%9D%E9%B8%A3%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B51.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>邬芝鸣</span>受伤的情况</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-9wyaf6QiqGY/UBpiqsZjO6I/AAAAAAAAKlM/YH-1izSpDog/s1600/%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%A4%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-9wyaf6QiqGY/UBpiqsZjO6I/AAAAAAAAKlM/YH-1izSpDog/s320/%E6%9B%BE%E6%AD%A3%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%A4%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>曾正会受伤情况</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-WGlqc8OuT1A/UBpi3cTcHmI/AAAAAAAAKlU/A1QGBBJwNy8/s1600/%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B0%9A%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%B2%E9%9B%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"229\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-WGlqc8OuT1A/UBpi3cTcHmI/AAAAAAAAKlU/A1QGBBJwNy8/s320/%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B0%9A%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%B2%E9%9B%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>至今尚在住院的母亲雷女士</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3595473390467104762?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}